<p>Remember that to calculate the area under the curve of <img src="//s0.wp.com/latex.php?latex=f%28x%29%3Dx%5E4&#038;bg=ffffff&#038;fg=000&#038;s=0" alt="f(x)=x^4" title="f(x)=x^4" class="latex" /> from, let&#8217;s say 2 to 5, we had to write:</p>
