<p>&#160;</p>
<p>And at that point we had barely even started because we still had to actually evaluate this sum, which is a hell of a calculation&#8230;then we have to calculate the limit. What a pain.</p>
<p>&#160;</p>
<p>Now, we are told that all we have to do is to find any antiderivative of <img src="//s0.wp.com/latex.php?latex=f%28x%29%3Dx%5E4&#038;bg=ffffff&#038;fg=000&#038;s=0" alt="f(x)=x^4" title="f(x)=x^4" class="latex" /> and we are basically done.</p>
