<p>Can we find a function which, when we take its derivative gives us <img src="//s0.wp.com/latex.php?latex=x%5E4&#038;bg=ffffff&#038;fg=000&#038;s=0" alt="x^4" title="x^4" class="latex" />?&#8230;</p>]]></description>
